<br />
I've never streamed anything, but I'm interested in helping new players learn to play DF. So, I've started streaming live as I play DF. I'm discussing, step by step, what I'm doing and why, and addressing the concerns that a new fortress undergoes. It's not structured except by chronology, and I've never streamed anything before, so I'm sure it's a little rough around the edges, but if you're curious, head on over and take a look. I'll answer any questions you guys have, whether here or at the reddit thread.<br />
<br />
I will say that I'm not sure I could do this for more than about four hours, though - my throat is tired.</blockquote>
